Description: Provides functionality for Hamiltonian Monte Carlo (HMC) regression models, 
    including initialization, parameter estimation, and MCMC chain building. The package 
    supports custom location and scale formulas, performs parameter fitting, and computes 
    credible intervals. It integrates Rcpp for high-performance computations.
